"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-8-9-indonesia-celebrates-first-olympic-golds-outside-badminton\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Golden day in Paris for Southeast Asian nation as speed climber Veddriq Leonardo and weightlifter Rizki Juniansyah win.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998562809754, \"rank\": 1.4371899013100972e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9999999842787021, \"rank\": 1.410630858287532e-08, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\"}, {\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Veddriq Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Speed climber Veddriq Leonardo has handed Indonesia its first Olympic gold outside badminton after sprinting up a 15-metre wall to beat his Chinese rival by just two-hundredths of a second.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 148, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Veddriq Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Veddriq_Leonardo\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9929222493107425, \"rank\": 0.007061482621002695, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.6333933531873636, \"rank\": 0.41275854872171036, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veddriq's gold was the first for Indonesia in theParis Olympics, and the ninth since the country made its Olympic debut in 1952.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9929222493107425, \"rank\": 0.007061482621002695, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel very happy, very joyful,\\\" the 27-year-old said.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My heart raced [in the competition], but I stayed focused and finished it.\\\"\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Veddriq scaled the wall in 4.75 seconds, a personal best, to pip China's Wu Peng for the top spot.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9742836985981714, \"rank\": 0.025563123808498466, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3735345179770454e-11, \"text\": \"Wu Peng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wu_Peng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His coach broke down in tears and Indonesian Sport Climbing Federation chairwoman Yenni Wahid said she was \\\"so moved I could cry\\\".\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 0.5746695477230414, \"rank\": 0.7337495759922779, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Indonesians celebrated Veddriq's Olympic victory, 21-year-old Rizki Juniansyah delivered the country's second gold of the day by winning the men's 73kg weightlifting competition.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.8382147509906157, \"rank\": 0.19301169398132723, \"text\": \"Indonesians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Juniansyah lifted a total of 354kg over the competition, winning the gold with an Olympic record clean and jerk of 199kg to beat his rivals from Thailand and Bulgaria.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999942044198321, \"rank\": 4.186350430612665e-06, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.974144955812915, \"rank\": 0.02641520557797048, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rizki said he was \\\"happy, proud and very emotional\\\" winning his first gold medal and thanked Indonesians for their support.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.8382147509906157, \"rank\": 0.19301169398132723, \"text\": \"Indonesians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are no words that can describe how I am feeling,\\\" the Jakarta Post reported the weightlifting as saying.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.832978797338263e-15, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You saw me crying because it's been such an emotional and beautiful experience and I am already looking toward the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Southeast Asian archipelago has become a major power in speed climbing, smashing records and nabbing multiple medals at top international events.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"score\": 0.9999999842787021, \"rank\": 1.410630858287532e-08, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Veddriq, who was born in Pontianak in Indonesian Borneo and took up the sport after joining a student nature group that also did wall climbing, has won the sport's World Cup three times and was the first speed climber to break the five-second barrier.\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pontianak\", \"score\": 0.9924104992623213, \"rank\": 0.007647541758206336, \"text\": \"Pontianak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pontianak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pontianak\"}, {\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalimantan\", \"score\": 0.9997745226108389, \"rank\": 0.00012637267112486302, \"text\": \"Borneo\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalimantan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalimantan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indonesian President Joko Widodo was among the first to congratulate him for the gold writing on X that the speed climber's achievement had brought \\\"new pride to Indonesia\\\".\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9999982769126129, \"rank\": 1.7230904530779273e-06, \"text\": \"Indonesian President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Indonesia\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joko_Widodo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joko Widodo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joko_Widodo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joko_Widodo\"}, {\"begin\": 2101, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9929222493107425, \"rank\": 0.007061482621002695, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The country had previously won golds only in badminton.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Words can hardly express how we feel.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Praise be to God,\\\" Veddriq's mother Rosita Hamzah told broadcaster Kompas TV.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kompas_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kompas TV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kompas_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kompas_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport climbing made its Olympics debut in Tokyo in 2021 but speed was controversially combined with the boulder and lead disciplines, which require completely different skill sets.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9980976360576339, \"rank\": 0.0018325230010281276, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris marks the first time speed specialists are competing in their own area of expertise.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998562809754, \"rank\": 1.4371899013100972e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud, very proud.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The excitement was explosive,\\\" Kristoforus Bagaskoro, a 41-year-old creative manager in the capital Jakarta, told the AFP news agency.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2687, \"end\": 2694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.832978797338263e-15, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}, {\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AFP news agency\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We should hype up this sport more and help it develop even more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sam Watson from the United States took bronze ahead of Iran's Reza Alipour in the climb for third place, recording a world record 4.74 seconds.\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2791, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Watson_(political_activist)\", \"score\": 0.8551999212394672, \"rank\": 0.16931216931219462, \"text\": \"Sam Watson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Watson_(political_activist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Watson_(political_activist)\"}, {\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6073559358664267, \"rank\": 0.6457121179572811, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2846, \"end\": 2850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999975957008955, \"rank\": 2.382810155061376e-06, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2853, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reza_Alipour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reza Alipour\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reza_Alipour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reza_Alipour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": []}]}"